# Environment Variables for RSVP System

# Add these to your deployment environment (Vercel, Netlify, etc.)
# DO NOT commit this file with real values to Git!

# Google Sheets Configuration (RECOMMENDED - Easier than Airtable!)
GOOGLE_SHEETS_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycbwr-zl-GPUbARd0XffQZlcEKOclQHMTBC8DUdgi3mpjY5-Pa8jfvLFIaLp6EPf4LU5JUQ/exec
GOOGLE_SHEETS_CSV_URL=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/e/2PACX-1vT8RZvLuq_IJov64TPRFXCZQ4bYyCQf5PnfeUqMOB4x1KGbYZRDMgH14QQ5IdlmsfaC6WuC-qTM-Ni6/pub?gid=0&single=true&output=csv

# Example values (replace with your actual URLs):
# GOOGLE_SHEETS_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/AKfycby.../exec
# GOOGLE_SHEETS_CSV_URL=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1ABC.../export?format=csv

# How to get these values:
# 1. Create Google Apps Script at script.google.com
# 2. Deploy as Web App with "Anyone" access
# 3. Create Google Sheet and publish as CSV
# 4. See GOOGLE_SHEETS_SETUP.md for detailed instructions

# Alternative: Airtable Configuration (if you prefer Airtable)
# AIRTABLE_API_KEY=your_airtable_personal_access_token_here
# AIRTABLE_BASE_ID=your_airtable_base_id_here

# Deployment Platform Instructions:
# - Vercel: Project Settings → Environment Variables
# - Netlify: Site Settings → Environment Variables  
# - Heroku: heroku config:set GOOGLE_SHEETS_URL=xxx